originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    t.production_year,
    r.role AS character_name,
    ct.kind AS company_type,
    COUNT(DISTINCT k.keyword) AS keyword_count
FROM 
    cast_info ci
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2023 
    AND ct.kind LIKE 'Producer%'
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, t.production_year, r.role, ct.kind
ORDER BY 
    keyword_count DESC, t.production_year DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."ACTOR_NAME", "t4"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t4"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t4"."CHARACTER_NAME", "t4"."COMPANY_TYPE", "t4"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "t4"."production_year" AS "production_year_"
FROM (SELECT MIN("s1"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", MIN("role_type"."role") AS "CHARACTER_NAME", MIN("company_type"."kind") AS "COMPANY_TYPE", COUNT(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword") AS "KEYWORD_COUNT", "title"."production_year"
FROM "cast_info"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "role_type" ON "cast_info"."role_id" = "role_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000 AND "title"."production_year" <= 2023 AND "company_type"."kind" LIKE 'Producer%'
GROUP BY "s1"."name", "title"."title", "title"."production_year", "role_type"."role", "company_type"."kind"
ORDER BY 6 DESC NULLS FIRST, "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"
